aceImage`` and surface the binary's exit code.\\n./forge/utility_scripts/native_test_verification.py:553:    Drives the ``runNativeTraceImage`` task per its contract\\n./forge/utility_scripts/native_test_verification.py:568:        \\\"runNativeTraceImage\\\",\\n./forge/utility_scripts/native_test_verification.py:570:        f\\\"-PtraceMetadataPath={run_dir}\\\",\\n./forge/utility_scripts/native_test_verification.py:595:                f\\\"runNativeTraceImage exceeded {timeout_seconds}s timeout\\\",\\n./forge/utility_scripts/native_test_verification.py:1010:    \\\"\\\"\\\"Return the per-class natively-collected output directory.\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n./forge/utility_scripts/native_test_verification.py:1019:        \\\"natively-collected\\\",\\n./forge/utility_scripts/native_test_verification.py:1030:    \\\"\\\"\\\"Return the global (non-class-scoped) natively-collected output directory.\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n./forge/utility_scripts/native_test_verification.py:1039:        \\\"natively-collected\\\",\\n./forge/tests/test_native_test_verification.py:46:            \\\"> Task :runNativeTraceImage\\\\n\\\"\\n./forge/tests/test_native_test_verification.py:331:            \\\"natively-collected\\\",\\n./forge/tests/test_native_test_verification.py:348:        When the invocation contains ``runNativeTraceImage``, the script\\n./forge/tests/test_native_test_verification.py:380:            if \\\"runNativeTraceImage\\\" in cmd:\\n./forge/tests/test_native_test_verification.py:386:                    (a.split(\\\"=\\\", 1)[1] for a in cmd if a.startswith(\\\"-PtraceMetadataPath=\\\")),\\n./forge/tests/test_native_test_verification.py:448:        self.assertFalse(any(\\\"runNativeTraceImage\\\" in c for c in calls))\\n./forge/tests/test_native_test_verification.py:481:        trace_calls = [call for call in calls if \\\"runNativeTraceImage\\\" in call]\\n./forge/tests/test_native_test_verification.py:722:            if \\\"runNativeTraceImage\\\" in cmd:\\n./forge/tests/test_native_test_v